{"tid":1377433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"面對速龍可以點打？","createTime":"2019-07-28T13:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:13:30.000Z","uid":77355,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc2b89f52c216a65ee7eb84c36396139702f411","tid":1377433,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:51:37.000Z","msg":"我睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed30091b9dc36321962835198d911625b512591e","tid":1377433,"uid":20291,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:53:40.000Z","msg":"要人多反壓夠勇就係咁，你一見就驚有撚用咩"},{"pid":"d0c4351864e83b8d07b3442c0a5264c093562dee","tid":1377433,"uid":28257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"靠近戰時人數優勢<br />\n<br />\n有冇人留意到，班狗策略變左，少左埋身近戰，一味催淚<br />\n<br />\n宜家不停咁放催淚彈，可能係因為每次班狗一打埋身戰都亂打人，發泄情緒，次次都比傳媒煲爆。宜家大家一定要有組織咁應對催淚彈，最好三人一小隊咁去滅彈。格離POST話，整濕衣件用黎包實成個彈亦不失為一個好方法。<br />\n<br />\n下次見速龍衝，唔好一下全部拔腿就跑，前線一下子崩潰，跟著有人就會落單，之前個個十幾人都咁樣係被捕。要反攻，四/五圍一都好，速龍係輕裝同主要做攻，防禦其實好低，同埋近攻時，佢地都射唔到催淚彈，一定中埋自己友。<br />\n<br />\n同埋一定要守到一條後路，唔好比人封死曬。"},{"pid":"d3e925dee8b62bc54e8782a0d65369639442a739","tid":1377433,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[728] 需要地方落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45920c2b215b9bacacc55fc87581c64671f7a07","tid":1377433,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:55:37.000Z","msg":"用油"},{"pid":"471bdb9d2d656bc5112548675176c38143ca760e","tid":1377433,"uid":47964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"身體對抗不足<br />\n唔夠狠"},{"pid":"02d1f8eea97b54af063720c66316d8212588bc0e","tid":1377433,"uid":199771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:56:29.000Z","msg":"人多就有得打"},{"pid":"4fd5f12e327af4f6e07ce80e8973330df7c4e113","tid":1377433,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b45920c2b215b9bacacc55fc87581c64671f7a07","tid":1377433,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:55:37.000Z","msg":"用油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"講左好多次冇咩用"},{"pid":"16a7f615adccdb82b52bb12b3de3781bf70072c9","tid":1377433,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c49747533d6ee287683ebedf0092f7df06bde88","tid":1377433,"uid":83927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"次次都咁被動 下次先攻  打散佢地先  全港30000萬幾隻狗<br />\n有冇1000隻速龍呀"},{"pid":"791da82456396196bf298c4193d5786fd75d6681","tid":1377433,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2672dde408476d83b2c691c8090ce45b5526c600","tid":1377433,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"即走 唔好落單<br />\n俾速龍捉到一會被打同壓鳩你落地下"},{"pid":"5ea624a6598bcdc700d22908f702919638fcaf53","tid":1377433,"uid":196861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"波子?"},{"pid":"e5e5ba0d34228b0013e9bad1bc2ca71e04d9aee3","tid":1377433,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ea624a6598bcdc700d22908f702919638fcaf53","tid":1377433,"uid":196861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"波子?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:12:24.000Z","msg":"冇用"},{"pid":"5df5ce03a011ea565f31aa70f6b6cf3d584a6c99","tid":1377433,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:13:30.000Z","msg":"冇得打快閃